    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS to achieve exceptional volumetric efficiency and an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry with polyurethane bushings. Power is transmitted via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal mechanical grip. This unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are operating at factory tolerances. Finished in pristine factory paint with a flawless interior, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
